CatDescriptText: Cutline for image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 27, 1954, pg. 11, reads: "The DD's Cocktail Party - Another portion of the party-going Dandy Duffers and their guests in the midst of the happy cocktail party they gave at the Flamingo Sunday evening. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Dandy Duffers golf club members and guests, including Marion Harris Slater seated on right, and Harold Slater standing second from right, posed at bar in Flamingo Club
